13
00:00:27.500 --> 00:00:30.633
Why don't you let Wan Qi live in your house?

14
00:00:30.900 --> 00:00:32.733
Aunt, it's not that you don't know

15
00:00:32.733 --> 00:00:34.266
Before I couldn't see it at all

16
00:00:34.300 --> 00:00:35.500
I can't tell you.

17
00:00:38.066 --> 00:00:39.300
But don't worry, aunt.

18
00:00:39.333 --> 00:00:42.366
