Thank you, you're welcome.

25
00:01:03.700 --> 00:01:05.700
In fact, I have been looking for you since I returned to China

26
00:01:05.700 --> 00:01:08.166
Yes, looking for me.

27
00:01:08.733 --> 00:01:10.200
After that trip

28
00:01:10.200 --> 00:01:11.700
