31
00:01:16.966 --> 00:01:18.233
But your phone keeps turning off

32
00:01:19.200 --> 00:01:20.166
Ah!

33
00:01:21.666 --> 00:01:24.433
That's because after I graduated, I

34
00:01:24.800 --> 00:01:27.400
Just go through work

35
00:01:27.400 --> 00:01:29.033
Changed the phone number

36
00:01:29.133 --> 00:01:30.433
I see.

37
00:01:31.333 --> 00:01:33.833
Fortunately, we finally meet again.

38
00:01:34.866 --> 00:01:36.666
I will never let you go again this time

